---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About Us | Yihazi" 
  description="Learn about the philosophy behind Yihazi Tool Box." 
  lang="en"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 p-8 md:p-12 text-gray-800 leading-relaxed">
      
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Vision</h1>
      <p class="mb-4">In an era full of bloatware cloud services, finding simple and pure utilities is challenging. "Yihazi," a Sichuan dialect word meaning "A split second," represents our dedication to saving you as much time as possible.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Technology & Open Source</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">Built with a completely transparent, open-source model utilizing <strong>Astro</strong> paired with <strong>React</strong> and <strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> for near zero-latency interactions.</p>
      <p>Everything is free. Drop us a star on <a class="text-brand-600 hover:underline" href="https://github.com/jenray/yihazi" target="_blank">GitHub</a>.</p>
      
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
